#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.88"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.88:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:0.2"
msgid "9. Theravagga "
msgstr "9. Senior Mendicants "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.88:0.3"
msgid "88. Assajisutta "
msgstr "88. With Assaji "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn22.88:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the squirrels’ feeding ground. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā assaji kassapakārāme viharati ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. "
msgstr "Now at that time Venerable Assaji was staying in a monastery built by a Kassapa, and he was sick, suffering, gravely ill. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā assaji upaṭṭhāke āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then he addressed his carers: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:1.4"
msgid "“etha tumhe, āvuso, yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamatha; upasaṅkamitvā mama vacanena bhagavato pāde sirasā vandatha: "
msgstr "“Please, reverends, go to the Buddha, and in my name bow with your head to his feet. Say to him: "

msgctxt "sn22.88:1.5"
msgid "‘assaji, bhante, bhikkhu ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. "
msgstr "‘Sir, the mendicant Assaji is sick, suffering, gravely ill. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:1.6"
msgid "So bhagavato pāde sirasā vandatī’ti. "
msgstr "He bows with his head to your feet.’ "

msgctxt "sn22.88:1.7"
msgid "Evañca vadetha: "
msgstr "And then say: "

msgctxt "sn22.88:1.8"
msgid "‘sādhu kira, bhante, bhagavā yena assaji bhikkhu tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’”ti. "
msgstr "‘Sir, please go to the mendicant Assaji out of compassion.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:1.9"
msgid "“Evamāvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato assajissa paṭissutvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "“Yes, reverend,” those monks replied. They did as he asked. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:1.10"
msgid "“assaji, bhante, bhikkhu ābādhiko … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.88:1.11"
msgid "sādhu kira, bhante, bhagavā yena assaji bhikkhu tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā”ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn22.88:1.12"
msgid "Adhivāsesi bhagavā tuṇhībhāvena. "
msgstr "The Buddha consented in silence. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.125, sc2
msgctxt "sn22.88:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yenāyasmā assaji tenupasaṅkami. "
msgstr "Then in the late afternoon, the Buddha came out of retreat and went to Venerable Assaji. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:2.2"
msgid "Addasā kho āyasmā assaji bhagavantaṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ. "
msgstr "Venerable Assaji saw the Buddha coming off in the distance, "

msgctxt "sn22.88:2.3"
msgid "Disvāna mañcake samadhosi. "
msgstr "and tried to rise on his cot. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: āyasmantaṃ assajiṃ → āyasmato assajissa (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn22.88:2.4"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ assajiṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "But the Buddha said to him, "

msgctxt "sn22.88:2.5"
msgid "“alaṃ, assaji, mā tvaṃ mañcake samadhosi. "
msgstr "“It’s all right, Assaji, don’t get up. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:2.6"
msgid "Santimāni āsanāni paññattāni, tatthāhaṃ nisīdissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "There are some seats spread out by others, I will sit there.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:2.7"
msgid "Nisīdi bhagavā paññatte āsane. Nisajja kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ assajiṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "He sat on the seat spread out and said, "

msgctxt "sn22.88:2.8"
msgid "“kacci te, assaji, khamanīyaṃ, kacci yāpanīyaṃ … pe … paṭikkamosānaṃ paññāyati no abhikkamo”ti? "
msgstr "“Assaji, I hope you’re keeping well; I hope you’re alright. And I hope the pain is fading, not growing, that its fading is evident, not its growing.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn22.88:3.1"
msgid "“Na me, bhante, khamanīyaṃ … pe … abhikkamosānaṃ paññāyati no paṭikkamo”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, I’m not all right, I’m not getting by. My pain is terrible and growing, not fading, its growing is evident, not its fading.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:3.2"
msgid "“Kacci te, assaji, na kiñci kukkuccaṃ na koci vippaṭisāro”ti? "
msgstr "“I hope you don’t have any remorse or regret?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:3.3"
msgid "“Taggha me, bhante, anappakaṃ kukkuccaṃ anappako vippaṭisāro”ti. "
msgstr "“Indeed, sir, I have no little remorse and regret.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:3.4"
msgid "“Kacci pana taṃ, assaji, attā sīlato na upavadatī”ti? "
msgstr "“I hope you have no reason to blame yourself when it comes to ethical conduct?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:3.5"
msgid "“Na kho maṃ, bhante, attā sīlato upavadatī”ti. "
msgstr "“No sir, I have no reason to blame myself when it comes to ethical conduct.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:3.6"
msgid "“No ce kira taṃ, assaji, attā sīlato upavadati, atha kiñca te kukkuccaṃ ko ca vippaṭisāro”ti? "
msgstr "“In that case, Assaji, why do you have remorse and regret?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:3.7"
msgid "“Pubbe khvāhaṃ, bhante, gelaññe passambhetvā passambhetvā kāyasaṅkhāre viharāmi, sohaṃ samādhiṃ nappaṭilabhāmi. "
msgstr "“Sir, before my time of illness I meditated having completely stilled the physical process. But now I can’t get immersion. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:3.8"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, taṃ samādhiṃ appaṭilabhato evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "Since I can’t get immersion, I think: "

msgctxt "sn22.88:3.9"
msgid "‘no cassāhaṃ parihāyāmī’”ti. "
msgstr "‘May I not decline!’” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:3.10"
msgid "“Ye te, assaji, samaṇabrāhmaṇā samādhisārakā samādhisāmaññā tesaṃ taṃ samādhiṃ appaṭilabhataṃ evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "“Assaji, there are ascetics and brahmins for whom samādhi is the essence, equating immersion with the ascetic life. They think: "

msgctxt "sn22.88:3.11"
msgid "‘no cassu mayaṃ parihāyāmā’ti. "
msgstr "‘May we not decline!’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.126, sc4
msgctxt "sn22.88:4.1"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, assaji, "
msgstr "What do you think, Assaji? "

msgctxt "sn22.88:4.2"
msgid "rūpaṃ niccaṃ vā aniccaṃ vā”ti? "
msgstr "Is form permanent or impermanent?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:4.3"
msgid "“Aniccaṃ, bhante” … pe … "
msgstr "“Impermanent, sir.” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:4.4"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "“Is consciousness permanent or impermanent?” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:4.5"
msgid "“tasmātiha … pe … "
msgstr "“So you should truly see … "

msgctxt "sn22.88:4.6"
msgid "evaṃ passaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Seeing this … "

msgctxt "sn22.88:4.7"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānātīti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: vedayati → vediyati (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn22.88:4.8"
msgid "So sukhañce vedanaṃ vedayati, sā ‘aniccā’ti pajānāti. ‘Anajjhositā’ti pajānāti. ‘Anabhinanditā’ti pajānāti. "
msgstr "If they feel a pleasant feeling, they understand that it’s impermanent, that they’re not attached to it, and that they don’t relish it. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:4.9"
msgid "Dukkhañce vedanaṃ vedayati, sā ‘aniccā’ti pajānāti. ‘Anajjhositā’ti pajānāti. ‘Anabhinanditā’ti pajānāti. "
msgstr "If they feel a painful feeling, they understand that it’s impermanent, that they’re not attached to it, and that they don’t relish it. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:4.10"
msgid "Adukkhamasukhañce vedanaṃ vedayati, sā ‘aniccā’ti pajānāti … pe … ‘anabhinanditā’ti pajānāti. "
msgstr "If they feel a neutral feeling, they understand that it’s impermanent, that they’re not attached to it, and that they don’t relish it. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:4.11"
msgid "So sukhañce vedanaṃ vedayati, visaṃyutto naṃ vedayati; "
msgstr "If they feel a pleasant feeling, they feel it detached. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:4.12"
msgid "dukkhañce vedanaṃ vedayati, visaṃyutto naṃ vedayati; "
msgstr "If they feel a painful feeling, they feel it detached. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:4.13"
msgid "adukkhamasukhañce vedanaṃ vedayati, visaṃyutto naṃ vedayati. "
msgstr "If they feel a neutral feeling, they feel it detached. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:4.14"
msgid "So kāyapariyantikañce vedanaṃ vedayamāno ‘kāyapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ vedayāmī’ti pajānāti. Jīvitapariyantikañce vedanaṃ vedayamāno ‘jīvitapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ vedayāmī’ti pajānāti. "
msgstr "Feeling the end of the body approaching, they understand: ‘I feel the end of the body approaching.’ Feeling the end of life approaching, they understand: ‘I feel the end of life approaching.’ "

msgctxt "sn22.88:4.15"
msgid "‘Kāyassa bhedā uddhaṃ jīvitapariyādānā idheva sabbavedayitāni anabhinanditāni sītībhavissantī’ti pajānāti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘When my body breaks up and my life is over, everything that’s felt, being no longer relished, will become cool right here.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn22.88:5.1"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, assaji, telañca paṭicca, vaṭṭiñca paṭicca, telappadīpo jhāyeyya; "
msgstr "Suppose an oil lamp depended on oil and a wick to burn. "

msgctxt "sn22.88:5.2"
msgid "tasseva telassa ca vaṭṭiyā ca pariyādānā anāhāro nibbāyeyya. "
msgstr "As the oil and the wick are used up, it would be extinguished due to lack of fuel. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.88:5.3"
msgid "Evameva kho, assaji, bhikkhu kāyapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ vedayamāno ‘kāyapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ vedayāmī’ti pajānāti. Jīvitapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ vedayamāno ‘jīvitapariyantikaṃ vedanaṃ vedayāmī’ti pajānāti. "
msgstr "In the same way, feeling the end of the body approaching, they understand: ‘I feel the end of the body approaching.’ Feeling the end of life approaching, they understand: ‘I feel the end of life approaching.’ "

msgctxt "sn22.88:5.4"
msgid "‘Kāyassa bhedā uddhaṃ jīvitapariyādānā idheva sabbavedayitāni anabhinanditāni sītībhavissantī’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘When my body breaks up and my life is over, everything that’s felt, being no longer relished, will become cool right here.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.88:5.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

